{"tid":375103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求剪頭髮都要「考牌」呀！","createTime":"2017-08-26T09:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T05:48:36.000Z","uid":5266,"like":1014,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0ea1f519d204ca699b377348c7fbf663aac2f7","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:28:00.000Z","msg":"屌 <br />\n呢家周街都係QB 速剪 仲有啲騎呢怪名另起爐灶<br />\n細時以前啲做街坊小店 就執q晒<br />\n呢家想方便落樓下剪個頭髮唯有去速剪喇<br />\n屌你老味 通常入去豪賭個頭前都會睇下啲師傅乜料<br />\n一係就金毛呀叔 仲要揸著包國產煙嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就啲大陸呀嬸 係到柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬 雖然你係平姐 但都唔好揾啲咁嘅師傅黎害人地個頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚大間公司唔該執嚴啲師傅嘅質素喇<br />\n剪到人唔三唔四點撚樣見人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我係今日嘅受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n正評：要考牌呀屌"},{"pid":"042a6e1781bac717f069e175386f09b92eefcd7f","tid":375103,"uid":66684,"like":1,"dislike":43,"score":-42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"無知一問 乜幫人剪頭髮唔係要考師傅牌嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138fadcf62510c0156e5e19126e8e3882d80df9","tid":375103,"uid":2207,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 <br />\n呢家周街都係QB 速剪 仲有啲騎呢怪名另起爐灶<br />\n細時以前啲做街坊小店 就執q晒<br />\n呢家想方便落樓下剪個頭髮唯有去速剪喇<br />\n屌你老味 通常入去豪賭個頭前都會睇下啲師傅乜料<br />\n一係就金毛呀叔 仲要揸著包國產煙嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就啲大陸呀嬸 係到柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬 雖然你係平姐 但都唔好揾啲咁嘅師傅黎害人地個頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚大間公司唔該執嚴啲師傅嘅質素喇<br />\n剪到人唔三唔四點撚樣見人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我係今日嘅受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n正評：要考牌呀屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAGGER<br />\n係外國有d 國家要考cert 先可以剪髮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cd514b09583544b939f49a3d526626f5bdbbac","tid":375103,"uid":11717,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"過日本剪"},{"pid":"5d6b3cff844a660cb55208386b851465ebf8d4af","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問 乜幫人剪頭髮唔係要考師傅牌嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔知<br />\n但我都唔覺得啲呀叔呀嬸都有牌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係亂鳩咁黎架"},{"pid":"1ad8a14882e7cff14df3dfd3563903b2be1761ef","tid":375103,"uid":130513,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cd9b496b7668b9eb224972c38aca951ba8d9c10","tid":375103,"uid":21149,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:38:30.000Z","msg":"出面正常個d都係一舊水多d姐 大約一個月剪一次<br />\n平幾十蚊柒足一個月 下個月又再柒過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8627e056c802ad4c0d279bb61c1041cef2aa1255","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出面正常個d都係一舊水多d姐 大約一個月剪一次<br />\n平幾十蚊柒足一個月 下個月又再柒過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n百幾蚊果啲其實都係博一博<br />\n效果可能同快剪差唔多<br />\n但真係堅果啲又幾百蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算喇 我諗其實都係人夾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c596abd6236b4f389632d654b06765c16dea6e43","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請自貼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢家去剪個快剪<br />\n一齊自貼比較下咩質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5f3f35e7d3c5b77fa987c1e9ead27446d234bc","tid":375103,"uid":109050,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:50:19.000Z","msg":"有d速剪真係痴撚線<br />\n完全無技巧又唔識用力<br />\n以為自己做監犯比人剃頭"},{"pid":"b70d41c3dd9edcd9a5dbc8fbf05faa9e59fc74c4","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d速剪真係痴撚線<br />\n完全無技巧又唔識用力<br />\n以為自己做監犯比人剃頭</blockquote><br />\n最快係可以5分鐘就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我俾佢剪完真係想直接剷晒成個頭算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbf2485a079b886eae5a72e0ffd687e1f2aa49e","tid":375103,"uid":33420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"樣的問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nqb house <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ac01456ae37e8c6f99af294712fb1d9a0b04aa","tid":375103,"uid":85431,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"qb香港係好差<br />\n應該向近小小既台灣qb學習<br />\n人地請埋班純情大波妹<br />\n攬住你黎慢慢同你逐條修<br />\n剪個咩頭都願啊"},{"pid":"59db2e46a1e7ebbc18fa5b18dd061060800a2cb2","tid":375103,"uid":60655,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"你有金城武咁靚仔<br />\n剷個河童頭都溝死女"},{"pid":"f347aba05dd0cf079ce1274f6b0999cba70d4b36","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>qb香港係好差<br />\n應該向近小小既台灣qb學習<br />\n人地請埋班純情大波妹<br />\n攬住你黎慢慢同你逐條修<br />\n剪個咩頭都願啊</blockquote><br />\n香港有大波妹幫我剪 <br />\n我一次買兩張票又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本係香港請埋啲人求其<br />\n培訓又是旦 搞歪晒呢個行業"},{"pid":"7a44f9fe425c02f5fa61b6fa7b8226805013b300","tid":375103,"uid":5266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"Uppp"},{"pid":"a18e9634c0c18c98661000794d27f343bfc877b2","tid":375103,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:15:57.000Z","msg":"次次去qb三分鐘剪完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ef7f776e65cc57f089d31aa8832273389064a9","tid":375103,"uid":140254,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"屌，仲要上埋與客人溝通了解改進課程，屌撚完剪咩野頭，剪撚完不似預期，跟著佢話ok嗎，我心諗屌你老味你都剪撚到咁仲有改變嘅餘地咩"},{"pid":"7fae7e254ba5351933df0ddc7240d0651ae9eba8","tid":375103,"uid":140254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，仲要上埋與客人溝通了解改進課程，屌撚完剪咩野頭，剪撚完不似預期，跟著佢話ok嗎，我心諗屌你老味你都剪撚到