/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09987e591065896e1a5dfbf9299c4631eeac8eec","tid":375103,"uid":117200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"日本剪頭髮要考牌，係個邊係一種專業黎<br />\n要讀大專上大學／去外國深造，厚生勞動省大臣先比張獎狀/許可証書你執業<br />\n人地連剪頭髮個層次都分十個Level,乜野角度,細節都寫晒係本book到,比你簡好晒先剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ddfadce99280570e82b5130bf834a3e925edb6e","tid":375103,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"開個剪髮學士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e6bd01f89237bb2d63fbc6b9102b039b4b18fb","tid":375103,"uid":52261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵開 係到出po 解答髮型問題位巴打 佢收既價錢同技術服務唔成正比 太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申打手</blockquote><br />\n幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n280</blockquote><br />\n絲打有冇髮型師嘅聯繫電話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我腥左email俾佢 但未覆"},{"pid":"1f372f885473947e2754926038c0fe8f181a0423","tid":375103,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>剪髮佬有煙味既話好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剪髮佬就成手煙屎，洗頭妹就成手精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026037c7effa69914712c3f831f5fcd58a09bf10","tid":375103,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"比貴少少啦<br />\n幾十蚊食個飯都無"},{"pid":"d3c49a5d49fd05b5e054b132e649a84de71613cc","tid":375103,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T03:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>剪髮佬有煙味既話好撚難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/