plyTime":"2017-08-27T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓下速剪4x 又平又好睇<br />\n究竟連登d人幾on9先講得出平=唔好<br />\n同d 無知c9一樣"},{"pid":"e467b87d71ab71889765a4f7ee5560b4fda73a5f","tid":375103,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:06:43.000Z","msg":"速剪真係好撚撞手神，怕中伏可以出面睇D先入去<br />\n後生打扮夠潮果D多數都唔會點柒<br />\n但試過一行入去有件短髮清潔阿姐咁款走出黎行埋位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後成個月唔敢見人"},{"pid":"277aa383015e69809193818f003ae9918e7fa27e","tid":375103,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"ok嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb62bbda938e88433930dd07c7585a769ce9a2c","tid":375103,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能毒撚對個頭冇要求 本身個頭又曲冇得留長<br />\n宜家剪親都係剪到好短 不是好彩搵到個岩心水既師父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭髮天生曲可能留長拉直<br />\n我個friend成日話qb師父剪得佢樣衰<br />\n我心諗俾咁少錢想要咩服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日訓到個頭扁晒又唔理<br />\n做兄弟果日都係咁<br />\n我心諗你根本就唔care,  又要成個怨婦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前都有keep住拉負離子 但天生真係曲得太勁 生返出黎果D曲到仆街<br />\n後尾索性放棄 兩邊剷青有咁高剷咁高 個頂偷簿剪短<br />\n寧願個人自信搭救算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aebe36bcec8e2c162007d0fe9a78453f083faa6","tid":375103,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"搵正常嗰啲髮型屋剪啦屌你<br />\n話到明速剪你想靚呀"},{"pid":"6bc1b8835fb6952760fb5f15f2916546cb7ff6c1","t